title: BaTi$_{2}$As$_{2}$O Structure
comments: \href{current_web_home_dir/A2BCD2_tP6_123_h_a_b_e-001}{BaTi$_{2}$As$_{2}$O} and \href{current_web_home_dir/ABC2D2_tP6_123_b_a_e_h-001}{CeCr$_{2}$Si$_{2}$C} are both in space group $P4/mmm$ \#123, and use the same Wyckoff positions.  They differ in the c/a ratio.  We follow the ICSD and put them into separate prototypes.
